      "Text": "Security update for helm",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for helm fixes the following issue\n\n- CVE-2026-48978: oras.land/oras-go/v2/registry/remote/auth: malicious registry can hijack Bearer token realm to\n  exfiltrate credentials and refresh tokens (bsc#1270127).\n\nChanges for helm:\n\n- Update to version 3.21.2.\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
